  "detailed_description": "The element race gifted on <strong>Element Release</strong> rules the ungifted slave, that is the way it has always been. But appearing of the <strong>Element Ring</strong> which makes anybody can <strong>Element Release</strong> breaks the mold. The rebellion of slaves raid a Water Territory of Element Empire. To cope with the situation, lord spells the Water Enchantment around the Water Territory.<br><br>As a memory loss prisoner of element race, involved in the fight, the most important things for you are defeating your enemies and escape...<br><br><strong>Element Release: Water Territory</strong> is an Action-Adventure singleplayer game, includes 1 level with big map, 13 weapons, 15 skills, over 30 collectable items, over 10 enemies, and 3 bosses. <br>Player will explore in a cartoony city, experience souls-like battles with innovative role growth and skill system.<br><br>Key features:<br>- Role growth and skill system basing on five element types<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2847590/extras/78e72eee74c9994f821e7fee0e405eaf.avif?t=1715766752\" width=480 height=270 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2847590/extras/204506f50ee47a82080010fc746aea64.avif?t=1715766752\" width=480 height=270 /></span><br><br>- Powerful skills intensified by <strong>Element Release</strong> and element intensifier<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2847590/extras/344d23ce07b67019134497386d0626a9.avif?t=1715766752\" width=480 height=270 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2847590/extras/508da9ed4e00fa7a9a2396de691259bc.avif?t=1715766752\" width=480 height=270 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2847590/extras/2c3d4dc1b0b3929f655522cb04325978.avif?t=1715766752\" width=480 height=270 /></span><br><br>- Collecting weapons, intensifiers, element rings, and consumables<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2847590/extras/5a978fccf41bab6c7c33bf9aa7051c5c.avif?t=1715766752\" width=480 height=270 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2847590/extras/4dd9e66d16c3f4c564c7a4bce76d427b.avif?t=1715766752\" width=480 height=270 /></span><br><br>- Calculating health and vitality, attacking, dodging, and taking advantage of skills, to defeat your enemies<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2847590/extras/360dfac78b26d1debe7368924fff4a37.avif?t=1715766752\" width=480 height=270 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2847590/extras/fd4d8358a8771e9f49e7d47a9bceaae2.avif?t=1715766752\" width=480 height=270 /></span><br><br>- Searching hidden path and shortcuts<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2847590/extras/a748183bb11445ad09e2bb1be513a8af.avif?t=1715766752\" width=480 height=270 /></span>",
